osing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Alice-Cooper">爱丽丝·库珀（Alice Cooper）</a> ，他的女儿印花布（Calico）和<a href="/artists/Slash">斜坡（Slash）</a>为他们的摩托车主题儿童歌曲“ Freewheelin”联手。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-alice-cooper-2450600"><b>摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ - 爱丽丝·库珀（Alice Cooper）</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>高能量的曲目看到爱丽丝和印花布唱<em>“我在新自行车上免费旋转了 /这是我喜欢的最好的东西 /现在您是自由地骑着自己的骑行，而无需任何帮助，可以更快地骑行，”</em>骑自行车时，斜线扔了一个令人振奋的吉他独奏。</p><p> “ Freewheelin”在格莱美奖提名的儿童专辑“ Solid Rock Revival”中出现。儿童摇滚是一个音乐集体，由爱丽丝和他的女儿以及沙龙·阿吉拉尔·卡米德，达娜·卡米德，梅卡·尼斯·尼斯·尼斯·尼斯·尼斯，瑞恩·伊恩斯，康拉德·瓦雷拉，约翰·戴维·威廉姆斯和鲁比·萨拉斯组成。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="儿童摇滚 -  freewheelin’（壮举。斜线，爱丽丝·库珀，印花布库珀）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1H9AO4514wc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “ Solid Rock Revival”在2025年格莱美颁奖典礼上获得了最佳儿童音乐专辑的提名，并以<a href="/artists/judgas-priest">Judas Priest</a>的<a href="/artists/rob-halford">Rob Halford</a> ， <a href="/artists/run-dmc">Run DMC</a>的Daryl“ DMC” McDaniels等为特色。 LP Benef Cooper的<a href="https://arizonansforchildren.org/mentorportal/teen-center/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solid Rock Teen Centers的</a>收益是一个非营利性组织，为12-20岁的青少年提供音乐，舞蹈，艺术等免费课后培训。</p><p>在谈到<a href="https://www.azcentral.com/story/entertainment/music/2024/11/13/alice-cooper-grammy-nomination-best-childrens-album/76198520007/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>亚利桑那共和国</em></a>的格莱美提名时，爱丽丝分享道：“爱丽丝·库珀（Alice Cooper）为儿童音乐获得格莱美奖不是最疯狂的事情吗？”</p><p>他继续说：“我认为这确实对[孩子们]说了一些东西。我们拥有一张可以赢得格莱美奖的专辑……对于孩子们来说，这是一件很酷的事情，看到成功的事物是一件很小的种子。有时，您为此而做的事情确实非常非常好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DArU1_TOjty/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,3